00:00:26.903 --> 00:00:29.306
Ciwanên bi hêrs,

00:00:29.330 --> 00:00:32.941
hawar, qerîn, qiyamet.

00:00:35.818 --> 00:00:37.306
Dînîtiya werzişê:

00:00:37.330 --> 00:00:40.306
girseyên mirovî ker dikin,

00:00:40.330 --> 00:00:45.051
hemû xebat ji bo gogê têxin torê de.

